cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper focuses on face alignment, which is a computer vision task related to facial recognition and analysis. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel deep learning model to jointly optimize multiple tasks, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely sub-categories as well. Additionally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on facial images, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
